{"_path":"/maps/_ai/operations/mlops","_dir":"operations","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"MLOps","description":"机器学习运维平台与工具，包括 Weights & Biases、MLflow、TensorBoard 等实验跟踪和模型管理方案。","original_path":"_ai/mlops.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"mlops"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLOps"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"weights-biases商业-mlops-平台事实标准"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Weights & Biases：商业 MLOps 平台事实标准"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"W&B 是商业 MLOps 平台的事实标准，提供实验跟踪、超参搜索、模型管理、协作报告等一站式能力。核心功能包括自动记录超参/指标/输出、Artifact 版本追踪、Sweeps 分布式超参搜索、交互式实验报告。是 LLM 微调实验跟踪的首选工具。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://wandb.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"W&B 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://wandb.ai/site/solutions/llm-fine-tuning/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"W&B LLM 专项功能"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://wandb.ai/site/experiment-tracking/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"W&B 实验跟踪"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"mlflow开源-ml-生命周期管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLflow：开源 ML 生命周期管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLflow 是 Databricks 开源的 MLOps 平台，模块化设计可独立使用各组件：Tracking（实验记录）、Projects（可复现工作流打包）、Models（模型格式标准化）、Registry（模型版本管理）。完全开源、自建托管，适合需要数据主权和成本控制的企业。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://mlflow.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLflow 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://mlflow.org/docs/latest/ml/model-registry/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLflow Model Registry"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/mlflow/mlflow","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLflow GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"tensorboard基础可视化工具"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TensorBoard：基础可视化工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TensorBoard 是 TensorFlow 配套的可视化工具，也支持 PyTorch（通过 torch.utils.tensorboard）。适合小规模实验快速可视化、训练曲线和学习率监控、嵌入向量降维可视化。轻量易用，是调试训练过程的常用工具。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.tensorflow.org/tensorboard","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TensorBoard 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llm-专项-mlops-挑战"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 专项 MLOps 挑战"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 带来独特挑战：模型文件巨大（7B 模型 14GB，版本管理困难）、训练周期长（需要断点续训和容错）、评估复杂（多维度基准测试）、对齐流程多阶段（SFT → DPO → RLHF）。解决方案包括模型注册表（MLflow Model Registry、W&B Artifacts）、分布式跟踪（Ray Train + W&B 集成）、评估集成（lm-eval-harness 结果自动记录）、Prompt 版本管理（W&B Prompts）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/tensorchord/Awesome-LLMOps","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLMOps 工具集"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.datacamp.com/blog/top-mlops-tools","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 MLOps 工具榜单"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"可重复性与实验管理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可重复性与实验管理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可重复性是 ML 系统的核心支柱，涉及随机种子固定、数据版本控制、环境容器化等关键实践。详见 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"./reproducibility"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ML 可重复性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"weights-biases商业-mlops-平台事实标准","depth":2,"text":"Weights & Biases：商业 MLOps 平台事实标准"},{"id":"mlflow开源-ml-生命周期管理","depth":2,"text":"MLflow：开源 ML 生命周期管理"},{"id":"tensorboard基础可视化工具","depth":2,"text":"TensorBoard：基础可视化工具"},{"id":"llm-专项-mlops-挑战","depth":2,"text":"LLM 专项 MLOps 挑战"},{"id":"可重复性与实验管理","depth":2,"text":"可重复性与实验管理"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:operations:mlops.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/operations/mlops.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/operations/mlops","_extension":"md"}